@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative Two

autonumber

actor "Owner" as Owner
participant ":System" as System

activate Owner

        Owner -> System : Click on the "Register" button
    activate System

        System --> Owner : Displays the registration form with its fields
    deactivate System

        Owner -> System : Types the requested data and submits the form
     activate System

        System --> Owner: Creates the user, alerts of the operation success \nand sends confirmation email
     deactivate System

        Owner -> System : Click on the verification link in the email
        activate System

        System --> Owner: Displays the verification form
    deactivate System

        Owner -> System : Click on the "Verify" button
    activate System

        System --> Owner: Verifies the user, alerts of the operation success \nand sends welcome email
    deactivate System

@enduml